ldings, Inc.\">HTZ</a></span>) due to its weak financial performance and growth which has led to poor stock performance. Over the last year, the stock has slumped by more than 40% underperforming the S&amp;P</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/926104828/image_926104828.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741646-hertz-global-holdings-weak-financially-and-lags-industry-trends", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:48:18"}, {"id": "4741644", "title": "Coupang's Emerging Opportunities: A Compelling Case For Investment", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coupang logo, sign on company headquarters in Silicon Valley.\" data-id=\"1355025074\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriorit