://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NejauPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Black swans aren\u2019t what they used to be.</p> <p>When ancient Roman satirist <a href=\"https://www.gutenberg.org/files/50657/50657-h/50657-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Juvenal coined the term</a> in the second century C.E., he was characterizing the perfect love interest. The idea was that black swans don\u2019t exist.</p> <p>Surprise!</p> <p>In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741641-atkore-stock-down-portion-of-black-swan-boom-be-worse-bust-cycle", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:32:17"}, {"id": "4741640", "title": "SCHO: Why I'm Writing About 4 Dollars", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt