nc.\">ARCO</a></span>) released 3Q24 earnings.</p> <p>The company's operations are still growing, with challenges only in Argentina, which is undergoing a deep recession. On the other hand, growth does not seem to be pushing margins up anymore.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741638-arcos-dorados-costs-are-delevering-not-a-great-sign-maintain-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 09:11:32"}, {"id": "4741637", "title": "NAD Vs. NXP Revisited: Time To Delever", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"On the table are pie charts, a pen and a folder with the inscription - Municipal bond.\" data-id=\"1253600459\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dzmitry Skazau</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Leveraged Funds Outperform In 2024 But Dividend Hikes May Have Been The Reason</h2> <p>It's been a year since I first <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4656162-nad-vs-nxp-leverage-quality-and-duration-in-muni-bond-funds\">compared leveraged and unleveraged municipal bond closed-end funds</a> using two examples from <a href=\"https://www.nuveen.com/en-us/closed-end-funds?assetclass=Municipal%20fixed%20income%20-%20National%20-%20High%20yield|||Municipal%20fixed%20income%20-%20National%20-%20Investment%20grade|||Municipal%20fixed%20income%20-%20National%20-%20Investment%20grade%20/%20high%20yield\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nuveen</a>. Leveraged funds were</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741637-nad-vs-nxp-revisited-time-to-delever", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 09:07:33"}, {"id": "4741636", "title": "BigCommerce Holdings: Growing E-Commerce Venture At A Cheap Price", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman doing online shopping for clothes on smartphone at home\" data-id=\"1814678203\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1